Lecture 10:  
Sasha Rakhlin 

Description 
We introduce bagging and boosting algorithms. We discuss the bias-variance tradeoff. 
The gradient descent view of boosting is introduced and a bound on the performance of 
Adaboost is proved.  

Suggested Reading 
•  Yoav Freund and Robert E. Schapire. A short introduction to boosting. 
